{"tid":1671240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"召集十萬天主教徒教徒  星期六下午遮打見","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:11:34.000Z","uid":335962,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0d16116e43cc4510fa41d5c9f64aaae530018f3f","tid":1671240,"uid":335962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭自稱天主教徒教徒，但縱容721元朗白衣人恐怖襲擊、黑警插贓嫁禍、新屋嶺雞姦事件，有違天主教徒教義、教理！<br />\n<br />\n現召集十萬天主教徒教徒，為受害人、為香港祈禱！感謝敢言的夏志誠輔理主教，抵抗一切壓力，守護我們的香港、我們的教會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「播種和平」玫瑰經祈禱會<br />\n<br />\n每年的十月是聖母玫瑰月，教會鼓勵我們在這個月勤念玫瑰經。讓我們在這個月偕同聖母，一起誦念玫瑰經，默觀正義和平的君王一耶穌基督，並為香港人的平安，為這城的民主和自由祈禱，祈求香港社會變得更仁愛和公義，更符合天主的旨意。<br />\n<br />\n 「播種和平」玫瑰經祈禱會<br />\n日期： 2019年 10月26日（六）<br />\n時間： 下午二時三十分<br />\n地點： 中環遮打花園<br />\n主禮：夏志誠輔理主教<br />\n<br />\n主辦：香港天主教正義和平委員會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaeoQkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaeoQkd.jpg&h=149f4081&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"077f248158946ef3c6533da63e9bc3b4f21068dd","tid":1671240,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"eebeafff4193b3064fc5379b53370f3c78343bde","tid":1671240,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"[極度緊急]急急急，英國領事館外面急要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d6913abca6b9600fd974ed8b1e3a47347471ea0","tid":1671240,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f7956eb86e1dad834d6d01abbb22514e91f097","tid":1671240,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"Respect <img src=\"/assets/fa